org.openhubframework.openhub.api.entity

Interface Node

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HumanReadable, Identifiable<Long>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNode, MutableNode

    public interface Node
extends HumanReadable, Identifiable<Long>
    Contains information about one node in cluster.

    Value of attributes in this entity can not be changed. If you want to change value of attributes (like code, name...), use MutableNode.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Roman Havlicek
    See Also:
    MutableNode
